  "body": "This Pull Request updates dependency [babel-plugin-module-resolver](https://github.com/tleunen/babel-plugin-module-resolver) from `v2.7.1` to `v3.0.0`\n\n\n### Commits\n\n<details>\n<summary>tleunen/babel-plugin-module-resolver</summary>\n\n#### 3.0.0\n-   [`278eb13`](https://github.com/tleunen/babel-plugin-module-resolver/commit/278eb132482776827e5de2d039cfe9c74228e48a) chore(release): 3.0.0\n-   [`47fd5ba`](https://github.com/tleunen/babel-plugin-module-resolver/commit/47fd5ba02f64aec22940285431aa8ed7af6df44a) feat: Add require.requireActual and require.requireMock to the list of transformed Jest functions (#&#8203;227)\n-   [`a7c04b0`](https://github.com/tleunen/babel-plugin-module-resolver/commit/a7c04b081a07058109353162a808a503ead53957) feat: Add jest.setMock to the list of transformed jest functions (#&#8203;225)\n-   [`ba978d8`](https://github.com/tleunen/babel-plugin-module-resolver/commit/ba978d8f18b8605b83547de2009d9ee836c92796) chore: Set name of plugin for eslint integration (#&#8203;226)\n-   [`7811238`](https://github.com/tleunen/babel-plugin-module-resolver/commit/78112389fdf5708f254a91120f200c4925c06db1) chore: Set node 6 as min version (#&#8203;222)\n-   [`3c711f8`](https://github.com/tleunen/babel-plugin-module-resolver/commit/3c711f802e1dc92c1eab137a8f5cf2c466bef496) feat: Make alias config take precedence over root config (#&#8203;221)\n-   [`0a16ea8`](https://github.com/tleunen/babel-plugin-module-resolver/commit/0a16ea8b75070d9aad06f5480ff2f0926bf5e4ff) chore: Update jest &amp; eslint airbnb (#&#8203;220)\n\n</details>\n\n\n\n---\n\nThis PR has been generated by [Renovate Bot](https://renovateapp.com).",
